com.gemalto.idp.mobile.qr.emv.transaction

Interface Template

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AdditionalDataFieldTemplate, MerchantInformationLanguageTemplate, TemplateWithGui

    public interface Template
extends DataObject
    Implementation of template data object type as defined by EMV specification. Template data object contains an inner structure of other templates or primitive data objects which could be retrieved by DataObject.getDataObjects() method.
    Since:
    5.0
